*Stižem* u pet ujutru. (I'm arriving at five in the morning.)

Sutra *stižem* kući. (I'm arriving home tomorrow.)

Večeras *stigao* sam kasno. (I arrived late tonight.)

*Stigla* sam u pet. (I arrived at five.)

*Stižemo* na vreme. (We're arriving on time.)

*Stigao* sam na vreme. (I arrived on time.)